
1. fill WebAPI credentials in config/alle_api.yml
2. set up description renderer in config/initializers/alle_api.rb
3. run migrations
4. include AlleApi::Categorizable into model that will be categorized with Allegro categories
5. include AlleApi::Auctionable into models that will be put into auctions
6. implement missing methods on your auctionables
  - #title_for_auction: this will be used as an auction title
  - #category_id_for_auction: this will be used to provide auction category
